🌟 Universel Beauty Training Academy Presents Tamil Nadu’s First-Ever Beautician Job Expo! 🌟
💄 Bridging Talent with Opportunity in the Beauty Industry! 💄

At Universel Beauty Training Academy, we believe in empowering beauticians with the skills and career opportunities they deserve. For years, we have been offering 100% job placement to students who complete their training at our institute. But we wanted to take it a step further – and so, we launched the first-ever Beautician Job Expo in Tamil Nadu!

🚀 What is the Beautician Job Expo? 🚀
The Beautician Job Expo is a revolutionary initiative where we bring together salon and parlour owners from all over Tamil Nadu to connect with talented beautician candidates. Unlike traditional job fairs, this expo provides live interviews, where candidates get the chance to showcase their skills and get selected for jobs on the spot!

✨ A Grand Success – The Job Expo Highlights ✨
📅 Dates: March 16th & March 23rd
📍 Location: Our Chennai branches in Tambaram & Perambur

🔹 Hundreds of aspiring beauticians from across Tamil Nadu participated
🔹 Top salon and parlour owners attended the event to hire fresh talent
🔹 Live interviews were conducted
🔹 Instant job offers were given to deserving candidates

🎊 The Results? A Career-Changing Experience! 🎊
This initiative has opened doors for numerous beauticians, helping them secure jobs in well-established salons and parlours. It was truly a historic moment for the beauty industry, and we are thrilled to have played a role in shaping so many careers!

🌟 What’s Next? More Job Expos Coming Soon! 🌟
Due to the overwhelming success of this event, we are excited to announce that we will be hosting more job expos across Tamil Nadu! If you missed this opportunity, stay tuned for our next event and take the first step towards a bright future in the beauty industry.

💖 At Universel Beauty Training Academy, we don’t just train – we create careers! 💖

📢 Follow us for updates on upcoming events! 📢
📞 Contact us for more details!
